Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:08.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:24.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:29.83,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:31.30,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:38.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather comes fluttering\ndown, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:45.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:54.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:01.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:08.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:15.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:23.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:28.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:41.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:48.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to bring the materials\nfor my presentation today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That really blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you leave them in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, I put it all together\nin a pile last night and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:57.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go fetch them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:58.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:09.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's he up to?{\i0}\NBelldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:14.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:22.97,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Living Under One Roof Together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:32.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever. If she can't find it,\nshe'll just come back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:36.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, Morisato. Did\NBelldandy dump you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:37.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you get dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, for god's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:46.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, you had a fight\nwith Bell-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:50.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit by myself for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everybody reacting this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:59.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem, Morisato?\NYou look depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:02.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:06.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So now you're joining in, too.\NBelldandy's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:11.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, Morisato. Getting yourself\nsuch a good-looking girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:16.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, Morisato. Getting yourself\nsuch a sweet girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:20.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, uh, Belldandy and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've already gone that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Den-chan!{\i0}\NDai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:33.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gladly bear the responsibility of\nfinding the right name for your child!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is not to be taken lightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get back to you after\ngiving it some serious thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:46.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A name...\NWhat kind of name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was pretty quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! Miss Mishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mr. Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual for you not\nto be with Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:11.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I left something at home,\nand she went back to get it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At home? You mean, your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See, I just got kicked out of the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you live alone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:25.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, not alone, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:38.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that you and Belldandy\nwere that involved already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:43.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Keep your\nvoice down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could say it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:54.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so sweet, but she's\nas bold as the next person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:59.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But look, we just live together, that's all.\NThere's really nothing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:03.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nothing going on?\NYou've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:09.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to kid about, and\nbesides, I think you got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy and I are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You two are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:18.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:21.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:25.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you! You're not\nin grade school anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to take it slow...\nnot jump into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:32.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With an attitude like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:36.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll never have a relationship with a\ngirl except in your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:42.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, considering you once dared to\nmake a bid for me, that girl should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...child's play for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:52.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing you have to do is\ntell her how you really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:57.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For the rest, you can come up\nwith it on your own, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:10.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,True, exactly what kind of\nrelationship are we in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty quick of you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:21.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I wasn't sure which ones you\nneeded, so I brought everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're heavy, so please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:37.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the thing is... you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:42.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:53.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The engine evolved as the double-valve\nsystem and was gradually improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:57.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Early engines used direct exhaust\nvalves with camshafts, valves...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:01.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and dual exhaust ports all\nresiding within the engine block.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:04.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She is pretty cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:08.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She did say she'd stay\nwith me forever, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:12.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that's just because of her\ncontract as a goddess, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no, not necessarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:19.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy hasn't shown any signs\nthat she doesn't want to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish I could find out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:25.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...tell her how you really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiichi? Keiichi?{\i0}\N...tell her how you really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...tell her how you really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:34.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. This is something that I\nhave to take the initiative on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Belldandy that I lo... lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:40.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You got that, Morisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you love cylinder heads\nto that extent, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:56.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:05.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had to go and do it, didn't I?\nI made a complete fool of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:12.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing is, I really\nam in love with Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:18.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just tell her how I feel,\nand all goes well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:36.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, come on. We are\nliving together, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can do something more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:43.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've warmed up the bed for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:54.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not right! I don't\nhave those depraved thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:59.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is for Belldandy\nto go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how do I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:16.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Should I just be straightforward\nand ask her to go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:20.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't work with Miss\NMishima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:36.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, isn't what I'm doing just\nanother form of ''night-creeping''?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:51.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it was going to come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:03.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...why didn't I just wish for her\nto be my girlfriend from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How could I shackle Belldandy\nwith a wish like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No other way but to go tell her myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:17.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, I can't do it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ne{\i0}xt{\i1}, this just in...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Late last night there was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Were you working on another report?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.\nI got so much done, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:41.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:46.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, since you have no classes today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:50.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I wish you'd slept in a\nlittle longer this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:55.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can take a nap later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:04.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go on\na museum tour with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That would be a breach of contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:17.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?\NKeiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:21.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have a call from Mr. Tamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:25.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I must've fallen asleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God it was just a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:31.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He said he had something\nimportant to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:32.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:39.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he was really\nthinking up names for our kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! Dinner will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:55.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's good-looking, she's sweet,\nand she's a great cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What else could a guy ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:01.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if I confess my feelings\nand it doesn't work out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:08.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:30.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I never want to lose\nsight of that smile of hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:47.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Easier said than done, though...\nwhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:52.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it would be better\nto take the right steps...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:56.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I got laughed at when I tried\nto go out with Miss Mishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like I have all\nthese techniques at my disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be around here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... lemme see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was it this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:14.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I could've sworn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:19.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, the seniors just\ndumped it all in every which way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:22.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it... hold it... found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:26.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The ''Surefire Techniques for Love''\nhow-to book I bought ages ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:33.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:38.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kisu? Would you like\nkisu fish for your dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:41.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it... forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll help you later on, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:56.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner will be ready soon.\nIt won't be much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:02.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:06.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nowhere near the kissing stage yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:13.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Confess your feelings at a restaurant\nthat has a beautiful night view...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:25.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid our establishment requires\nformal wear for all its patrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:36.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can just\nhave dinner right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should confess in\na romantic environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with beautiful music\nplaying in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:15.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known that was\ntoo much to ask of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:30.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly what you'd\ncall romantic, huh? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Found 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Candles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:43.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, better than nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I need some romantic music.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:07.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy metal, Western pop singers,\nstand-up comedy, rakugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:10.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and unidentifiable folk music.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:14.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I guess I'm not\nthe romantic type of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:22.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:27.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:34.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy, come to think of it, you can\nread peoples' minds, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:40.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! That means my plans to\nconfess were all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:44.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Although I can only see your\nemotions as different colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I have to really look for it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:54.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An angry person appears to be red...\nblue when he's sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:57.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it as a\nvague whirlpool of colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:01.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, Keiichi seems a bit blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's back to yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:07.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My powers as a goddess have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:12.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...significantly limited. I no longer need\nto serve as an emotional antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:16.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?\NThat's all I need to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:20.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner is ready now,\nso please come to the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:24.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there, so\njust hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:33.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know I had this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:47.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know, it must be the seniors'.\nIt got thrown in by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Great, this is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:08.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see orange, he's a bit excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...or nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:14.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Keiichi,\nis something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, nothing's the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:31.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi is all yellow\nwith joy now. I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:35.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:46.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... could you come with me\nsomewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My, how lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:57.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all set to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:19:01.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do now is tell Belldandy\nhow I feel about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:11.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? My seniors\nsetting me up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:16.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was I thinking,\ngoing by that how-to book?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:20.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with just being myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen\nto make Keiichi sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:28.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now he's orange again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:40.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know it must sound weird to say this\nwhen we're living together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I just want to be\nup front about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:49.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heart rate 150 bpm, blood pressure 170!{\i0}\nI have something I want to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And still on the rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:55.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His temperature's 101! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you must rest now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, I'm not sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:27.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your pulse is racing and you have a\nfever. Your blood pressure's surging!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:33.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is red and you're sweating.\NThis is what they call illness, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:44.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to lose consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I can't let this stop me from...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...tell Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:11.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:16.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do\nwith the contract, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:23.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just like any guy and girl, I want you\nto go out with me, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:25.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:33.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you've been acting\nso strange since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:39.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I came\nto you on a mission from...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Heavenly System.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:49.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no more deceit in\nmy feelings than there is in yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:52.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be happy, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:57.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that's more than a feeling...\nit is my own wish for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:03.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:06.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I should've seen it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:11.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we go out, or don't go out,\nor how it looks to other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:15.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter,\nbecause after all, Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, then, Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:19.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:24.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is going to stay with me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:39.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:51.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:23:00.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:07.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:13.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:16.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:22.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:29.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:35.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:41.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:45.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.61,0:24:01.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The young girl has left her hometown\nto make a new start in a new land.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:05.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not knowing that she might shatter the\npeaceful life of a goddess and a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.85,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode:\NAh! A Blessing in Every Bargain?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.85,0:24:12.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? We have to go\nhouse-hunting again?
